        "generateUrl": "https://app.tavily.com",
        "setup": "Sign up or log in at [Tavily app](https://app.tavily.com) and create/get your API key. Tavily docs describe using it as a Bearer token like `Authorization: Bearer tvly-YOUR_API_KEY`, and the docs repeatedly link to [Get your free API key](https://app.tavily.com).",
